				<section class="box special">
					<header class="major">
						<h2>Discover the injusticies you face everyday
						<br />
						by using propietary software</h2>
						<p>Most of the people in the digital age go about their lives being used by proprietary, sole-owned and sole-controlled software, without ever taking into account the injustices their ignorance brings upon themselves. The alternative to using freedom-denying software is free software, or libre software. Free software respects users' freedom and supports the libre software ecosystem and community. The users have the freedom to run, copy, distribute, study, change and improve the software.</p>
					</header>
					
